A Research Fellow position under School of Biological Sciences is available in the laboratory of Dr Yonggui Gao, located in EMB-NTU, Singapore.

Job Description

  Work on molecular mechanism of plant biomass synthesis and its regulation


Job Requirements

  PhD in Biological Sciences
  Candidates with good motivation and experience in both biochemical and structural expertise in the relevant field are encouraged to apply
  Structural skills, protein expression (Bacterial and Baculovirus system)/purification would be preferred


We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.